scenes.description: Amelia Watson reacts to a 'Teammates Fanbook' and community messages while playing with a mini claw machine.

subtitles.original: Then, thank you for all the birthday wishes...
subtitles.english: Then, thank you for all the birthday wishes...

subtitles.original: ...and thank you for all the memberships. And thank you, thank you, thank you.
subtitles.english: ...and thank you for all the memberships. And thank you, thank you, thank you.

subtitles.original: Without you guys, I wouldn't have been able to get this far celebrating our third birthday together.
subtitles.english: Without you guys, I wouldn't have been able to get this far celebrating our third birthday together.

subtitles.original: Is it our third birthday together? Our third one? So...
subtitles.english: Is it our third birthday together? Our third one? So...

subtitles.english: Thank you so very much!

subtitles.english: Yes, wow. Our third birthday together. It went by pretty fast, though.

subtitles.original: It went by pretty fast!
subtitles.english: It went by pretty fast!

subtitles.original: Alright, so take a look at this fanbook. I don't know, some of you guys may have contributed.
subtitles.english: Alright, so take a look at this fanbook. I don't know, some of you guys may have contributed.

subtitles.original: I think there's a scroll function here.
subtitles.english: I think there's a scroll function here.

subtitles.original: Oh yeah! Whoa, don't look, don't look, don't look, don't look! I'm just kidding. I'll let you guys look just for today, okay?
subtitles.english: Oh yeah! Whoa, don't look, don't look, don't look, don't look! I'm just kidding. I'll let you guys look just for today, okay?

subtitles.original: Wow, look how pretty! Our illustration by Ardenlolo.
subtitles.english: Wow, look how pretty! Our illustration by Ardenlolo.

subtitles.original: Ah, it's it's it's it's... Ow! Foreword: Teammates Case File No. 002.
subtitles.english: Ah, it's it's it's it's... Ow! Foreword: Teammates Case File No. 002.

subtitles.original: This book was made for the one and only Amelia Watson, including content from the VRC map portion of the project.
subtitles.english: This book was made for the one and only Amelia Watson, including content from the VRC map portion of the project.

subtitles.original: I don't know if we'll be able to look at the VRC map today. I'm not sure if we'll have any time.
subtitles.english: I don't know if we'll be able to look at the VRC map today. I'm not sure if we'll have any time.

subtitles.original: But, um, yeah, I definitely want to take a look at it on stream at some point. Yeah, yeah, yeah, that'd be really fun.
subtitles.english: But, um, yeah, I definitely want to take a look at it on stream at some point. Yeah, yeah, yeah, that'd be really fun.

subtitles.original: Messages within this book from teammates are for the eyes, only for the eyes of Ame.
subtitles.english: Messages within this book from teammates are for the eyes, only for the eyes of Ame.

subtitles.original: Wait, does that mean I can't stream it? Oh well, you guys are you guys are put on the spot now!
subtitles.english: Wait, does that mean I can't stream it? Oh well, you guys are you guys are put on the spot now!

subtitles.original: Put on the spot now!
subtitles.english: Put on the spot now!

subtitles.original: Front cover art, rear cover art, page design, assets. Thank you, thank you!
subtitles.english: Front cover art, rear cover art, page design, assets. Thank you, thank you!

subtitles.original: Only one copy of the book will be printed, which will be sent to you, Ame #1237.
subtitles.english: Only one copy of the book will be printed, which will be sent to you, Ame #1237.

subtitles.original: That's me! Uh-oh, just in case this one has been lost in another timeline, burnt by Small Ame, stolen by Bee Ame, etc.
subtitles.english: That's me! Uh-oh, just in case this one has been lost in another timeline, burnt by Small Ame, stolen by Bee Ame, etc.

subtitles.original: Yes, the digital copy. You guys are all put on the spot now!
subtitles.english: Yes, the digital copy. You guys are all put on the spot now!

subtitles.original: To all Ames who have their birthday on January 6th, this project was made and compiled especially for you by teammates all over the globe.
subtitles.english: To all Ames who have their birthday on January 6th, this project was made and compiled especially for you by teammates all over the globe.

subtitles.original: This is our way to say thank you for all that you do for us. You mean a lot to every teammate, and this is our way to show it.
subtitles.english: This is our way to say thank you for all that you do for us. You mean a lot to every teammate, and this is our way to show it.

subtitles.original: Whoa, everyone involved has worked incredibly hard to make this gift, which goes to show how special this community is that you've built...
subtitles.english: Whoa, everyone involved has worked incredibly hard to make this gift, which goes to show how special this community is that you've built...

subtitles.original: ...and all the values and inspirations you've given us. Whoa, you guys are too nice.
subtitles.english: ...and all the values and inspirations you've given us. Whoa, you guys are too nice.

subtitles.original: Here, here, let me help you guys out. Hold on. For those of you guys still playing, trying to get every item...
subtitles.english: Here, here, let me help you guys out. Hold on. For those of you guys still playing, trying to get every item...

subtitles.original: I think there's some pretty rare items in there that you guys haven't gotten yet in the claw machine.
subtitles.english: I think there's some pretty rare items in there that you guys haven't gotten yet in the claw machine.

subtitles.original: Excuse me... Grab! What is it?
subtitles.english: Excuse me... Grab! What is it?

subtitles.original: Whoa, my hat! You guys have got that one already. How many of those do you need? Do you each need a hat? Is that it?
subtitles.english: Whoa, my hat! You guys have got that one already. How many of those do you need? Do you each need a hat? Is that it?

subtitles.original: Uh, okay, let's see. As mentioned before, this project also includes the 3D VRC map...
subtitles.english: Uh, okay, let's see. As mentioned before, this project also includes the 3D VRC map...

subtitles.original: ...so we hope you can check it out if you have some time. This book contains the art from that map, but we still hope you check the map out.
subtitles.english: ...so we hope you can check it out if you have some time. This book contains the art from that map, but we still hope you check the map out.

subtitles.original: Whoa! We apologize for any kind of scruff you might find in the book, we hope you enjoy your gift nonetheless.
subtitles.english: Whoa! We apologize for any kind of scruff you might find in the book, we hope you enjoy your gift nonetheless.

subtitles.original: It's okay, scruff is par for the course. Par for the course.
subtitles.english: It's okay, scruff is par for the course. Par for the course.

subtitles.original: Hold on, let me drink some water though. You guys having fun?
subtitles.english: Hold on, let me drink some water though. You guys having fun?

subtitles.original: Par for the EN course, right? Oh, my magnifying glass!
subtitles.english: Par for the EN course, right? Oh, my magnifying glass!

subtitles.original: Ah! Papaya! Uh, teammates always look forward to spending more time with you...
subtitles.english: Ah! Papaya! Uh, teammates always look forward to spending more time with you...

subtitles.original: ...and we can't wait to see more of your achievements in the future. Oh, thank you. Oh, cute! Shuzzo!
subtitles.english: ...and we can't wait to see more of your achievements in the future. Oh, thank you. Oh, cute! Shuzzo!

subtitles.original: By Shuzzo! Whoa, hi, hi, hi, hi, hi!
subtitles.english: By Shuzzo! Whoa, hi, hi, hi, hi, hi!

subtitles.original: Don't look, don't look! And a message... Ah, sorry, I think my computer's lagging a little bit. Here we go.
subtitles.english: Don't look, don't look! And a message... Ah, sorry, I think my computer's lagging a little bit. Here we go.

subtitles.original: Thank you for always bringing joy to everyone with your stream. I can't express how much we appreciate your hard work on trying to push the boundaries of EN Vtubing...
subtitles.english: Thank you for always bringing joy to everyone with your stream. I can't express how much we appreciate your hard work on trying to push the boundaries of EN Vtubing...

subtitles.original: ...setting up collabs with your coworkers. Me personally, you were my first time someone used my art for a thumbnail...
subtitles.english: ...setting up collabs with your coworkers. Me personally, you were my first time someone used my art for a thumbnail...

subtitles.original: ...and gave me the greatest joy and motivation to continue grinding my art skill. I'm happy to see how much you've grown well since debut.
subtitles.english: ...and gave me the greatest joy and motivation to continue grinding my art skill. I'm happy to see how much you've grown well since debut.

subtitles.original: Oh, that's so sweet. Thank you! Ah, I'm happy that you let me use your art for a thumbnail. That's so sweet. Thank you, thank you.
subtitles.english: Oh, that's so sweet. Thank you! Ah, I'm happy that you let me use your art for a thumbnail. That's so sweet. Thank you, thank you.

subtitles.original: Ame, you are awesome beyond comprehension, truly a one of a kind human, even if you are British.
subtitles.english: Ame, you are awesome beyond comprehension, truly a one of a kind human, even if you are British.

subtitles.original: Kidding aside, you have gone beyond measure in your endeavors as an idol, a detective, and a friend.
subtitles.english: Kidding aside, you have gone beyond measure in your endeavors as an idol, a detective, and a friend.

subtitles.original: I wish you the happiness of all timelines combined and please know that no matter into what adventure you get into, your investigation will be behind...
subtitles.english: I wish you the happiness of all timelines combined and please know that no matter into what adventure you get into, your investigation will be behind...

subtitles.original: ...cheering and supporting you all the way! Oh, thank you!
subtitles.english: ...cheering and supporting you all the way! Oh, thank you!
